<item>
            <title>[HBASE-11214] Fixes for scans on a replicated table</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-11214</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;During testing with the IT in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-10818&quot; title=&quot;Add integration test for bulkload with replicas&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-10818&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-10818&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, found an issue to do with how &quot;close&quot; of scanners was handled. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
